<form>
<p class="MsoNormal"><font color="#3333FF"><b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-size: 16.0pt; font-family: Arial">筛选器</span><span style="font-size: 16.0pt; font-family: Arial">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <a href="javascript:print();"><img border="0" src="../image/Printer.gif" align="center" width="82" height="44"></a></span></b></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">&nbsp;使用<i>筛选器</i>屏幕可以阻止或允许特定类型的 Internet 使用。您可以设置特定 PC 的 Internet 访问策略，并通过使用网络端口号来设置筛选器。</span></p>  
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">&nbsp;</span></p>
<table class="MsoNormalTable" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="border-collapse: collapse; border-style: none; border-width: medium" height="1047">
  <tr>
    <td width="115" valign="top" style="width: 86.4pt; border: 1.0pt solid windowtext; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm" height="756">
<p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">Internet 访问策略</span></b></td>  
    <td width="475" valign="top" style="width: 356.4pt; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: medium; border-right: 1.0pt solid windowtext; border-top: 1.0pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1.0pt solid windowtext; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm" height="756">
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">使用此功能可以为特定 PC 定制多达十个不同的 Internet 访问策略，这些 PC 可使用其 IP 或 MAC 地址进行标识。对于为 PC 指定的每项策略，应指定日期和时段</span><span style="font-family:Arial">。</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">要创建或编辑策略，请遵循以下指导：</span></p>  
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:18.0pt">
    <span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; margin-left: 18.0pt">
<span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">1.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">在下拉菜单中选择策略编号 (1-10)。 </span></p>  
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; margin-left: 18.0pt">
<span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">2.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">在<i>输入配置文件名称</i>字段中输入名称。</span></p>  
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; margin-left: 18.0pt">
<span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">3.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">单击<b>编辑 PC 列表</b>按钮。 </span></p>  
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; margin-left: 18.0pt">
<span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">4.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">在<i>PC 列表</i>屏幕上，通过 IP 地址或 MAC 地址指定 PC。在 <i>IP</i> 字段中输入相应的 IP 地址。如果已有要筛选的 IP 地址范围，请完成相应的 <i>IP 范围</i>字段。在 <i>MAC</i> 字段中输入相应的 MAC 地址。 </span></p>  
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; margin-left: 18.0pt">
<span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">5.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">单击<b>应用</b>按钮可保存所做的更改。单击<b>取消</b>按钮可取消未保存的更改。单击<b>关闭</b>按钮可返回到<i>筛选器</i>屏幕。</span></p>  
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; margin-left: 18.0pt">
<span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">6.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">如果要在指定的日期和时间内阻止列出的 PC 进行 Internet 访问，则保留默认设置<b>禁止列出的 PC 进行 Internet 访问</b>。如果要在指定的日期和时间内使列出的 PC 可以访问 Internet，则单击<i>允许列出的 PC 进行 Internet 访问</i>旁边的单选按钮。</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; margin-left: 18.0pt">
<span style="font-family: Arial">7</span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">设置将筛选访问的日期。选择<b>每天</b>或一周中适当的几天。 </span></p>  
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; margin-left: 18.0pt">
<span style="font-family: Arial">8</span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;"></span></span><span style="font-family:Arial">&nbsp; </span> <span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">设置将筛选访问的时间。选择 <b>24 小时</b>，<b></b>或选中<i>从</i>旁边的框，并使用下拉框来指定特定的时段。 </span></p>  
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; margin-left: 18.0pt">
<span style="font-family: Arial">9</span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;"></span></span> <span style="font-family: Arial; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 7.0pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">单击<b>添加到策略</b>按钮可保存所做的更改</span><span style="font-family:Arial">并激活它。</span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial"> </span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; margin-left: 18.0pt">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:Arial">10</span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;"></span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">要创建或编辑其他策略，请重复步骤 1 到 </span><span style="font-family:Arial">9</span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">。</span></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td width="115" valign="top" style="width: 86.4pt; border-left: 1.0pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1.0pt solid windowtext; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: medium; border-bottom: 1.0pt solid windowtext; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm" height="36">
<p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">删除</span></b></td>
    <td width="475" valign="top" style="width: 356.4pt; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: medium; border-right: 1.0pt solid windowtext; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: medium; border-bottom: 1.0pt solid windowtext; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm" height="36">
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">要删除 Internet 访问策略，请选择策略编号，然后单击<b>删除</b>按钮。</span></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td width="115" valign="top" style="width: 86.4pt; border-left: 1.0pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1.0pt solid windowtext; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: medium; border-bottom: 1.0pt solid windowtext; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm" height="93">
<p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">摘要</span></b></td>
    <td width="475" valign="top" style="width: 356.4pt; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: medium; border-right: 1.0pt solid windowtext; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: medium; border-bottom: 1.0pt solid windowtext; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm" height="93">
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">要查看所有策略的摘要信息，请单击<b>摘要</b>按钮。<i>Internet 策略摘要</i>屏幕将显示每个策略的编号、策略名称、日期和每天的时间。要删除策略，请单击其框，然后单击<b>删除</b>按钮。单击<b>关闭</b>按钮可返回到<i>筛选器</i>屏幕。</span></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td width="115" valign="top" style="width: 86.4pt; border-left: 1.0pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1.0pt solid windowtext; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: medium; border-bottom: 1.0pt solid windowtext; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm" height="57">
<p class="MsoNormal"><b><span style="font-family: Arial" lang="ZH-CN">阻止的服务</span></b></p> 
    <p class="MsoNormal"></p>
    </td>
    <td width="475" valign="top" style="width: 356.4pt; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: medium; border-right: 1.0pt solid windowtext; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: medium; border-bottom: 1.0pt solid windowtext; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm" height="57">
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Arial" lang="ZH-CN">您可以选择阻止对某些服务的访问。单击“添加/编辑服务”可修改这些设置。</span></td> 
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td width="115" valign="top" style="width: 86.4pt; border-left: 1.0pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1.0pt solid windowtext; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: medium; border-bottom: 1.0pt solid windowtext; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm" height="26">
<p class="MsoNormal"><b><span style="font-family: Arial" lang="ZH-CN">通过 URL 阻止网站</span></b></p> 
    </td>
    <td width="475" valign="top" style="width: 356.4pt; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: medium; border-right: 1.0pt solid windowtext; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: medium; border-bottom: 1.0pt solid windowtext; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm" height="26">
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Arial" lang="ZH-CN">通过输入网站的 URL 可以阻止对某些网站的访问。</span></td>  
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td width="115" valign="top" style="width: 86.4pt; border-left: 1.0pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1.0pt solid windowtext; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: medium; border-bottom: 1.0pt solid windowtext; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm" height="67">
<p class="MsoNormal"><b><span style="font-family: Arial" lang="ZH-CN">通过关键字阻止网站</span></b></p>
    </td>
    <td width="475" valign="top" style="width: 356.4pt; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: medium; border-right: 1.0pt solid windowtext; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: medium; border-bottom: 1.0pt solid windowtext; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm" height="67">
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Arial" lang="ZH-CN">通过网页中包含的关键字可以阻止对某些网站的访问。</span></td>  
  </tr>
</table>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">选中所有值并单击<b>保存设置</b>可保存您的设置。单击<b>取消设置</b>按钮可取消未保存的更改。</span></p>  
<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
<center><input type="button" value="关闭" name="B3" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt" onClick=self.close()></center></p>
</form>
